## Release Tracking

### GitHub Actions Integration

```yaml
- name: Sentry Release
  uses: getsentry/action-release@v1
  env:
    SENTRY_AUTH_TOKEN: ${{ secrets.SENTRY_AUTH_TOKEN }}
    SENTRY_ORG: your-org
    SENTRY_PROJECT: your-project
  with:
    environment: production
    version: ${{ github.sha }}
    sourcemaps: ./dist
